==English==

===Noun===
'''dance'''
# (Sequence of) [[movement]]s to [[music]].
# a place where dancing is designed to take place (a school dance, for example)
# ''(heraldry)'' A [[fess]] that has been modified to [[zig-zag]] across the center of a [[coat of arms]] from [[dexter]] to [[sinister]].

